org.fest.swing.fixture
Class JTabbedPaneFixture

java.lang.Object
  org.fest.swing.fixture.ComponentFixture<JTabbedPane>
      org.fest.swing.fixture.JTabbedPaneFixture

public class JTabbedPaneFixture
extends ComponentFixture<JTabbedPane>

Understands simulation of user events on a JTabbedPane and verification of the state of such JTabbedPane.

Author:
Alex Ruiz, Yvonne Wang
